## Remarks  
 <span data-ttu-id="e64e3-137">包含表达式的预设值 (如果存在)。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e64e3-137">Contains the preset value of an expression, should one exist.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e64e3-138">例如, 如果表达式是<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Controls%2A>引用属性<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button>的属性引用表达式, 则<xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.ExpressionContext.PresetValue%2A>属性包含<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Controls%2A>属性的实例。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e64e3-138">For example, if the expression is a property reference expression referring to the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Controls%2A> property of a <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Button>, the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.ExpressionContext.PresetValue%2A> property contains the instance of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Controls%2A> property.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e64e3-139">这是因为属性是只读的, 由对象预设以包含一个值。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e64e3-139">This is because the property is read-only and preset by the object to contain a value.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e64e3-140">另一方面, 属性 ( <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text%2A>如或<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Visible%2A> ) 没有<xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.ExpressionContext.PresetValue%2A>预设值, 因此属性返回`null`。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e64e3-140">On the other hand, a property such as <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Text%2A> or <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Control.Visible%2A> does not have a preset value and therefore the <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.ExpressionContext.PresetValue%2A> property returns `null`.</span></span>  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e64e3-141">下面C#的代码演示了序列化程序如何使用此信息来引导序列化。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e64e3-141">The following C# code shows how serializers can use this information to guide serialization.</span></span>  
  
```csharp  
Padding p = new Padding();  
p.Left = 5;  
button1.Padding = p;  
  
button1.Padding.Left = 5;  
```  
  
 <span data-ttu-id="e64e3-142">如果应生成第<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Padding>一个或第二个窗体, 则需要通知结构的序列化程序。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e64e3-142">The serializer of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Padding> structure needs to be informed if it should generate the first or second form.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e64e3-143">默认情况下, 将生成第一个窗体。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e64e3-143">The first form is generated by default.</span></span> <span data-ttu-id="e64e3-144">仅当上下文堆栈<xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.ExpressionContext>上存在<xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.ExpressionContext.PresetValue%2A>包含等于当前要序列化的<xref:System.Windows.Forms.Padding>值的时, 才生成第二个窗体。</span><span class="sxs-lookup"><span data-stu-id="e64e3-144">The second form is only generated if there is an <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.ExpressionContext> on the context stack that contains a <xref:System.ComponentModel.Design.Serialization.ExpressionContext.PresetValue%2A> equal to the value of the <xref:System.Windows.Forms.Padding> currently being serialized.</span></span>
